USAGE:

1. Identify what you want to do

2. Setup variables in conf/DEFINES.conf

3. Create chain files in conf/chains. Use EXAMPLE.chain.sample as template chain.

4. (advanced, optional step) Define additional routing tables in /etc/iproute2/rt_tables
and assign ip route rules in iproute2/iproute2.(start|stop)

5. Restart firewall using p9-firewall restart command ran inside screen(1).
